The paper discusses recent advances in deep learning and proposes a novel Hierarchical Q-Network (HQN) for reinforcement learning. The paper also draws on theories of the hierarchical organization of the human prefrontal cortex. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the use of combinatorial games, which suggests a possible fit with cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
